<A>__{coming out of the blustery skies at the end of another deadly day, a squadron of spitfires chirps in for landings. the planes are shot up and battered. rafe is one of the pilots; the fuselage below his cockpit is marked with four swastikas, symbols of his victories. he taxis to a stop, and is met by ian, a scottish mechanic, who is dismayed at the state of the plane.}
